OL,3,CBoy, 12, accused of sex attack on
OL,4,Cwoman in her 60s to face trial in
OL,5,CBirmingham
OL,7,FA 12-year-old boy accused of sexually
OL,8,Fassaulting and wounding a woman aged
OL,9,Fin her 60s will face trial in October
OL,10,Fthis year, a court has heard.
OL,12,FThe youth was not asked to enter any
OL,13,Fpleas to the charges and unrelated
OL,14,Fallegations of intentional
OL,15,Fstrangulation and theft during a video-
OL,16,Flink appearance at Birmingham Crown
OL,17,FCourt.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
