OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776863482
OL,3,CBoy, 12, accused of sex attack on
OL,4,Cwoman in her 60s to face trial in
OL,5,CBirmingham
OL,7,FThe boy was charged by police last
OL,8,Fmonth with attacking a woman at an
OL,9,Faddress in Birmingham. She was taken
OL,10,Fto hospital and described as being in
OL,11,Fa serious condition.
OL,13,FJudge Simon Drew KC further remanded
OL,14,Fthe boy into secure accommodation
OL,15,Fafter a 20-minute hearing on Tuesday.
OL,17,FThe boy, who cannot be identified in
OL,18,Fmedia reports due to his age, was not
OL,19,Frequired to speak during the hearing,
OL,20,Fwhich was watched by his parents from
OL,21,Fthe public gallery.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776863482
OL,3,CBoy, 12, accused of sex attack on
OL,4,Cwoman in her 60s to face trial in
OL,5,CBirmingham
OL,7,FAdjourning the case, Judge Drew
OL,8,Fordered a plea and trial preparation
OL,9,Fhearing to take place in August.
OL,11,FThe judge added: "The next hearing
OL,12,Fthat I can definitely say will take
OL,13,Fplace will be on the 13th of August
OL,14,Fand the case will be listed for trial
OL,15,Fon October 5th."
